<title>普京：“胜利日停火”已开始生效</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E8%83%9C%E5%88%A9%E6%97%A5%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E2%80%9D%E5%B7%B2%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88</link>
